A reference implementation for Scene Management under Moai SDK.

Functions:
push ("sceneName") -> Pushes a scene
pop() -> Removes topmost scene
swap ("sceneName") -> Removes topmost scene, then pushes scene

Files:
main.lua -> Window Setup and Init
reflareLib.lua -> Our Misc helper functions
start.lua -> first scene
scene.lua -> scene management library
demo.lua -> second scene
display.lua -> Helper functions by Andrew Scott (https://github.com/anddrewscott/Moai-work/)